title: Parking to be improved at Big Hill Primary School (Greater Bendigo City Council)
text: ( Source : Greater Bendigo City Council ) Thursday October 15 , 2015 The Greater Bendigo City Council has voted to allocate funds in its 2016/17 budget for more and improved parking at the Big Hill Primary School at this week's Council meeting.
